---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Facilitator Guide Excerpt, Basecamp Retail"
  description="A representative spread from the Basecamp Retail facilitator guide, the keystone deliverable of the blended curriculum."
>
  <section class="bg-cream-50">

    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 sm:py-20">
      <a href="/case-studies/basecamp-retail" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm font-semibold text-cocoa/70 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors mb-6">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7" />
        </svg>
        Back to the case study
      </a>

      <p class="font-display text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-accent-700 mb-3">
        Basecamp Retail · Facilitator Guide
      </p>
      <h1 class="font-display font-semibold text-cocoa text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl leading-tight tracking-tight">
        A spread from the <span class="italic text-accent-600">keystone</span> deliverable.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-cocoa/70 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
        The full guide is 28 pages, spiral-bound, designed to be used on the sales floor. This is a representative two-page spread covering one of the four conversation moves, plus the pocket job aid it connects to.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>


  <section class="bg-cream-50 py-12 sm:py-16 border-t border-cocoa/10">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">

      <!-- Spread preview -->
      <div class="guide">
        <div class="guide__spread">
          <!-- Left page -->
          <article class="guide__page">
            <header class="guide__page-hd">
              <div>
                <p class="guide__chapter">Chapter 03 · The four-part conversation</p>
                <h2 class="guide__h1">The Fit Check</h2>
              </div>
              <div class="guide__page-num">p. 14</div>
            </header>

            <p class="guide__lede">
              The fit check is the move most associates skip. It's the bridge between "I think I know what you want" and "let me make sure I got that right before we commit the next thirty minutes."
            </p>

            <section class="guide__section">
              <h3>Purpose</h3>
              <p>Confirm you understood the customer's needs before recommending a specific SKU. Catches misreads, invites correction, and earns the right to recommend.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="guide__section">
              <h3>Scripted opening</h3>
              <blockquote class="guide__quote">
                "Before I show you the specific bikes, let me check that I've got this right. You ride mostly on paved paths with some light gravel, you want to cover about 15 miles a day, and you want something that'll still be comfortable a year from now. Did I hear that correctly?"
              </blockquote>
            </section>

            <section class="guide__section">
              <h3>Why this wording</h3>
              <ul class="guide__list">
                <li><strong>"Before I show you"</strong>, signals you're slowing down on purpose</li>
                <li><strong>Three specifics</strong>, enough to show you listened, short enough to stay in memory</li>
                <li><strong>"A year from now"</strong>, reframes from purchase to relationship</li>
                <li><strong>"Did I hear that correctly?"</strong>, open-ended, invites correction</li>
              </ul>
            </section>
          </article>

          <!-- Right page -->
          <article class="guide__page">
            <header class="guide__page-hd">
              <div>
                <p class="guide__chapter">Chapter 03 · The four-part conversation</p>
                <h2 class="guide__h1">Role-play setup</h2>
              </div>
              <div class="guide__page-num">p. 15</div>
            </header>

            <section class="guide__section">
              <h3>Run the drill (15 min)</h3>
              <ol class="guide__ol">
                <li>Pair associates. One is the <em>associate</em>, one is the <em>customer</em>.</li>
                <li>Deal one <strong>Customer Card</strong> to the customer (face down to the associate).</li>
                <li>Associate runs the first three moves (Open, Story, Needs). At the fit-check moment, they <strong>pause</strong> and deliver the scripted opening above.</li>
                <li>Customer confirms or corrects. Associate adjusts.</li>
                <li>Swap roles. Deal a new card.</li>
              </ol>
            </section>

            <section class="guide__section">
              <h3>Debrief questions</h3>
              <ul class="guide__list">
                <li>What did you change between what you thought they wanted and what they actually wanted?</li>
                <li>What body language shifted when they corrected you?</li>
                <li>How did <em>starting</em> with a fit check change the rest of the conversation?</li>
              </ul>
            </section>

            <div class="guide__callout">
              <p class="guide__callout-hd">Watch for</p>
              <p>
                Associates who breeze past the fit check because they "got it right." Push them to see the check as a <strong>reps</strong> move, it works even when the summary is correct, because the customer experiences being heard.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="guide__footer-meta">
              <span>Basecamp · The Four-Part Conversation</span>
              <span>v2.3 · For facilitator use</span>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Job aid -->
      <div class="jobaid">
        <div class="jobaid__hd">
          <p class="jobaid__eyebrow">Pocket job aid · double-sided · laminated</p>
          <h2 class="jobaid__h2">The Four-Part Conversation</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="jobaid__cards">
          <div class="jobaid__card">
            <span class="jobaid__num">01</span>
            <h3>Open</h3>
            <p>Within 15 seconds. Ask something that requires more than a yes.</p>
            <p class="jobaid__ex">"What's the bike going to do for you?"</p>
          </div>
          <div class="jobaid__card">
            <span class="jobaid__num">02</span>
            <h3>Story</h3>
            <p>Listen for the use case. Don't interrupt to correct specs.</p>
            <p class="jobaid__ex">"Tell me about the last ride that felt great."</p>
          </div>
          <div class="jobaid__card jobaid__card--accent">
            <span class="jobaid__num">03</span>
            <h3>Fit check</h3>
            <p>Summarize in three specifics. Invite correction before recommending.</p>
            <p class="jobaid__ex">"Did I hear that correctly?"</p>
          </div>
          <div class="jobaid__card">
            <span class="jobaid__num">04</span>
            <h3>Recommend + follow-up</h3>
            <p>Two options, not five. Ask permission to follow up in a week.</p>
            <p class="jobaid__ex">"Can I check in Thursday?"</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-6 text-center text-sm text-cocoa/55">
        Representative excerpt, typography and layout reflect the print production. Full guide + job aid + observation rubric were produced as a single bound package for 200+ stores.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .guide {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid rgba(85, 56, 36, 0.15);
      border-radius: 1.25rem;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 50px -20px rgba(85, 56, 36, 0.25);
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .guide__spread {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      min-height: 640px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 820px) { .guide__spread { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

    .guide__page {
      padding: 36px 40px 28px;
      background: #FBF4E2;
      color: #2E1F14;
      font-family: "Fraunces", Georgia, serif;
      position: relative;
    }
    .guide__page + .guide__page {
      border-left: 1px dashed rgba(85, 56, 36, 0.2);
    }
    @media (max-width: 820px) {
      .guide__page + .guide__page { border-left: 0; border-top: 1px dashed rgba(85, 56, 36, 0.2); }
    }
    @media (max-width: 560px) { .guide__page { padding: 24px 22px; } }

    .guide__page-hd {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-end;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #D9A441;
      padding-bottom: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .guide__chapter {
      font-size: 11px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: rgba(85,56,36,0.55);
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 0 0 4px;
    }
    .guide__h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1.9rem;
      color: #553824;
      line-height: 1.15;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }
    .guide__page-num {
      font-size: 11px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      color: rgba(85,56,36,0.5);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .guide__lede {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #553824;
      margin: 0 0 22px;
    }
    .guide__section { margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .guide__section h3 {
      font-size: 11.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      color: #A9522F;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-family: "Fraunces", Georgia, serif;
    }
    .guide__section p {
      margin: 0 0 6px;
      color: rgba(85,56,36,0.82);
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 0.98rem;
    }
    .guide__quote {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      background: #fff;
      border-left: 3px solid #D9A441;
      border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;
      font-style: italic;
      color: #553824;
      line-height: 1.55;
      font-size: 0.98rem;
    }
    .guide__list, .guide__ol {
      margin: 0; padding-left: 20px;
      color: rgba(85,56,36,0.82);
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 0.96rem;
    }
    .guide__list li, .guide__ol li { margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .guide__list strong, .guide__ol strong { color: #553824; font-weight: 600; }

    .guide__callout {
      background: rgba(217, 164, 65, 0.15);
      border: 1px solid rgba(217, 164, 65, 0.4);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      margin-top: 18px;
    }
    .guide__callout-hd {
      font-family: "Fraunces", Georgia, serif;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 11.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      color: #B8872F;
      margin: 0 0 4px;
    }
    .guide__callout p:last-child {
      margin: 0;
      color: rgba(85,56,36,0.82);
      line-height: 1.55;
      font-size: 0.94rem;
    }

    .guide__footer-meta {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 20px; left: 40px; right: 40px;
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between;
      font-size: 10.5px;
      font-family: "Fraunces", Georgia, serif;
      color: rgba(85,56,36,0.45);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    }
    @media (max-width: 560px) { .guide__footer-meta { left: 22px; right: 22px; bottom: 12px; } }

    /* Job aid */
    .jobaid {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2E1F14 0%, #553824 100%);
      color: #FBF4E2;
      border-radius: 1.25rem;
      padding: 28px 32px 32px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 50px -20px rgba(46, 31, 20, 0.4);
    }
    @media (max-width: 560px) { .jobaid { padding: 22px; } }
    .jobaid__hd { margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .jobaid__eyebrow {
      font-family: "Fraunces", Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 11px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: #D9A441;
      margin: 0 0 4px;
    }
    .jobaid__h2 {
      font-family: "Fraunces", Georgia, serif;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1.75rem;
      color: #FBF4E2;
      margin: 0;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }
    .jobaid__cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .jobaid__card {
      background: rgba(251, 244, 226, 0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(251, 244, 226, 0.16);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 16px;
      position: relative;
    }
    .jobaid__card--accent {
      background: rgba(217, 164, 65, 0.18);
      border-color: rgba(217, 164, 65, 0.4);
    }
    .jobaid__num {
      font-family: "Fraunces", Georgia, serif;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 22px;
      color: #D9A441;
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .jobaid__card h3 {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-family: "Fraunces", Georgia, serif;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #FBF4E2;
    }
    .jobaid__card p {
      margin: 0 0 6px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: rgba(251, 244, 226, 0.8);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .jobaid__ex {
      font-style: italic;
      color: rgba(251, 244, 226, 0.6) !important;
      font-size: 12px !important;
      border-top: 1px dashed rgba(251, 244, 226, 0.2);
      padding-top: 6px;
      margin-top: 8px !important;
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
